as of may31, 2010, the total gross unrecognized tax benefits, excluding related interest and
penalties, were $282.1 million, $158.4 million of which would affect the companys effective tax rate if recognized in future periods. total gross unrecognized tax benefits, excluding interest and penalties, as of may31, 2009 was $273.9
